00:32:30,470 --> 00:32:39,139
So, Kevin sees that from the tower.

406
00:32:39,139 --> 00:32:44,230
And in his own words, he went down the stairs
and had a little cry.

407
00:32:44,230 --> 00:32:48,779
Amazingly, there were survivors.

