00:33:24,489 --> 00:33:27,950
Yes you can.

416
00:33:27,950 --> 00:33:32,470
It comes in, the right wing tips at the last
minute.

417
00:33:32,470 --> 00:33:36,590
They couldn't control this.

418
00:33:36,590 --> 00:33:41,759
The right wing hits, spills fuel.

419
00:33:41,759 --> 00:33:43,309
The tail brakes off.

420
00:33:43,309 --> 00:33:47,049
The aircraft flips up.

